### Coding Standards

While we all may have different views of what is the best way to program something, we need standardization.  To that end, we will be using coding standards.

All R code will follow the [Google R Style Guide](http://google-styleguide.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/Rguide.xml).

SAS code will use TBD.

Standard headers can be found in each folder for a particular language

### Getting the Files

The entire set of files can be downloaded as a zip file by clicking the button ``Download ZIP'' in the lower left hand corner.

